{"tid":1322432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊齊幫狗絕育","createTime":"2019-07-16T02:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:55.000Z","uid":77089,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"229ed35df71b70c51df562482341c6d3d9294eb3","tid":1322432,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"大家都知狗主專登唔幫狗帶狗繩<br />\n要佢地落單咬人 明顯想借死狗翻盤<br />\n當見到狗單落 唔好亂踢  要瞄準位 幫佢地絕育<br />\n踢啱位 只要一下 隻狗就痛到郁唔到（真係一下就得）<br />\n咁做唔會打死狗 但又可以做到優生<br />\n只有惡狗先會亂咬人 絕後就冇劣種狗<br />\n再者 狗乸發情就一定控制唔到自己 <br />\n會四圍求偶交配 咁到時狗園又葬唔到 狗乸又走路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58df29e929c4b14eee285145e523ddcbd66471d1","tid":1322432,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01862139eaa6f34b751d09e2939bfd5e75e93f76","tid":1322432,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51854734803618952f13dace0faae4e20cca598","tid":1322432,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"全民幫狗絕育"},{"pid":"c8fd64467435895b69feee1d68b744939847ddf8","tid":1322432,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c04e1aec58205239f9245d942aa3ea855d0144f8","tid":1322432,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"."}]}